[center][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/105791.gif[/img][/center]
[center]Welcome to InsanityX development [Development team needed][/center]
[center][img]http://i910.photobucket.com/albums/ac308/garfdore/intro.png[/img][/center] InsanityX its a great & stable server , i have been coding all by my own as i have no coders at all this is my 1st project . InsanityX has 474 & 525 gameframe , I have always been dreaming of hosting my own RSPS project because when i play other people server , i feel that i wanna make my own server & let others enjoy but finally till this day i did it :D if you have a big dream or small dream it doesnt matter , all you have to do is GO FOR IT !
[center][u]Server Features[/u][/center]
[center] Skills are working stable 100% overloads Spirit shields with invincible strength bonuses Chaotic melee weapons , arcane stream neck , staff of light & added primal items Slayer task with slayer points reward&shop New donator zone (Working on it) Added donator ticket , point ticket & donator box set Working duel arena & staking 95% working godwars (only need to fix same subboses) Donator & staff capes with stats ! Custom whips with cool gfx SPECS ! 100% working clue scrolls Working minigames Many more ~ [/center]
